title: Double Trouble 2022: Giants & Eagles
description:
Field Yates, Mike Clay and Daniel Dopp round out the NFC East Double Trouble with the Giants and Eagles. Find out how to manage Saquon Barkley and Miles Sanders and if Jalen Hurts can be a Top 5 QB.
